Cannot run program "/home/coding/workspace/server/plugins/SakuraFrp/sakura_frpc": error=13, Permissi ...
Permission Denied 是由于缺少可执行权限
你可以安装这个插件：http://www.mcbbs.net/thread-801621-1-1.html
然后手动执行命令：chmod +x /home/coding/workspace/server/plugins/SakuraFrp/sakura_frpc
